#<AdxTL>@(#)0.0.0.0 $Revision$
# Superviseur
# Gestion du masque SIWRKEPV 

$_AFF
If GIMPORT
 Gosub AFF From GSAISIE
Else
 If GMESSAGE <>""
  Gosub ERR From GSAISIE
 Else
  Raz GERR , GZNUM
 Endif
Endif
Return

$HORODAT
Local Date    A_DATE
Local Char    A_HEURE(10) , A_USER(10)
Local Char    A_STAMP(15)
A_DATE  = [09/11/2018]
A_HEURE = "23:06:29"
A_USER  = "DOC"
A_STAMP = "20181109230629"
Return

$TITRES
Return

$CHG_FMT
Case zoncou
 When "NBADR"
  If [M]NBADR=0
  Endif
 When "NBVAT"
  If [M]NBVAT=0
  Endif
 When "NBFAC"
  If [M]NBFAC=0
  Endif
 When "NBLIG"
  If [M]NBLIG=0
  Endif
 When "NBEAV"
  If [M]NBEAV=0
  Endif
Endcase
Return

$VISU
Local Integer A_REPONSE
Global Integer GPRE_VIEW
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Mask SIWRKEPV [SIW0]
Gosub HORODAT
Local Inpbox "SIWRKEPV" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [SIW0] As [SIM_]
Grizo [SIW0]5
Grizo [SIW0]10
Grizo [SIW0]20
Grizo [SIW0]25
Grizo [SIW0]30
Grizo [SIW0]35
Boxact [SIM_]
Gosub TITRES
Boxinp [SIM_] Using A_REPONSE
Close Local Inpbox [SIM_]
Close Local Mask [SIW0]
Kill GPRE_VIEW
Return

$HARDCOP
Local Integer X1(0..14),X2(0..14),Y1(0..14),Y2(0..14)
X1(0)=1 : X2(0)=112 : Y1(0)=1 : Y2(0)=4
X1(1)=1 : X2(1)=112 : Y1(1)=5 : Y2(1)=12
X1(2)=1 : X2(2)=112 : Y1(2)=13 : Y2(2)=16
X1(3)=1 : X2(3)=112 : Y1(3)=17 : Y2(3)=20
X1(4)=1 : X2(4)=112 : Y1(4)=21 : Y2(4)=24
X1(5)=1 : X2(5)=112 : Y1(5)=25 : Y2(5)=28
Return

$ON_DATPIE
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_DATPIE From W1SIWRKEPV
Return

$AV_DATPIE
Chgfmt [M]DATPIE(indice) With "DPZ:"+GFMDAT
Gosub _AFF
Return

$ON_CUR
Return

$ON_ZCUR
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_ZCUR From W1SIWRKEPV
Return

$AV_ZCUR
Call LECTEXTRA(zc,"TABCUR","INTSHO",num$([M]CUR(indice)),"") From ATEXTRA
Gosub _AFF
Return

$ON_VACBPR
Return

$ON_ZVACBPR
