Gosub _AFF
Return

$ON_BPCNUM
Return

$ON_ADR1
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_ADR1 From W1SIWRKEPV
Return

$AV_ADR1
## Action FMTADRPAY
Call FMTADRPAY("") From TRTDIV
If GFMT<>""
 Chgfmt [M]ADR1(indice) With "KP:"+GFMT
Else
 Chgfmt [M]ADR1(indice) With "-K:1X"
Endif
Gosub _AFF
Return

