$ON_CRY
Onevent INIT_AREA Call D_CRY(zc) From W1SIWRKEPV
Return

Subprog D_CRY(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
If varinit([M]CRY,indice)=0
 VALEUR = GPAYS
Endif
Gosub _AFF
End

$ON_CRYNAM
Return

